    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Table Padding"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To control the space between the border and the content in a table, use the \npadding property on \n<td> and <th> elements:"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "data": [
        [
          "First Name",
          "Last Name",
          "Savings"
        ],
        [
          "Peter",
          "Griffin",
          "$100"
        ],
        [
          "Lois",
          "Griffin",
          "$150"
        ],
        [
          "Joe",
          "Swanson",
          "$300"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "th, td\n{\n   \npadding: 15px;  text-align: left;\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Horizontal Dividers"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "data": [
        [
          "First Name",
          "Last Name",
          "Savings"
        ],
        [
          "Peter",
          "Griffin",
          "$100"
        ],
        [
          "Lois",
          "Griffin",
          "$150"
        ],
        [
          "Joe",
          "Swanson",
          "$300"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Add the border-bottom property to <th> and <td> for horizontal dividers:"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "th, td {  border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Hoverable Table"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Use the :hover selector on <tr> to highlight table rows on mouse \nover:"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "data": [
        [
          "First Name",
          "Last Name",
          "Savings"
        ],
        [
          "Peter",
          "Griffin",
          "$100"
        ],
        [
          "Lois",
          "Griffin",
          "$150"
        ],
        [
          "Joe",
          "Swanson",
          "$300"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "tr:hover {background-color: coral;}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Striped Tables"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "data": [
        [
          "First Name",
          "Last Name",
          "Savings"
        ],
        [
          "Peter",
          "Griffin",
          "$100"
        ],
        [
          "Lois",
          "Griffin",
          "$150"
        ],
        [
          "Joe",
          "Swanson",
          "$300"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "For zebra-striped tables, use the nth-child() selector and add a background-color to all even (or odd) table rows:"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "tr:nth-child(even) {background-color: #f2f2f2;}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Table Color"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The example below specifies the background color \nand text color of \n<th> elements:"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "data": [
        [
          "First Name",
          "Last Name",
          "Savings"
        ],
        [
          "Peter",
          "Griffin",
          "$100"
        ],
        [
          "Lois",
          "Griffin",
          "$150"
        ],
        [
          "Joe",
          "Swanson",
          "$300"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "th {  background-color: #04AA6D;  color: white;}"
        }
      ]
    },
